Data Access Object (DAO) layer explanation

Responsibilities

- Connect to the database (MYSQL, H2, OracleSQL, etc)
- Also called the Repository/Persistence layer, 
- Inject the service interface/class, and call the service class/method in the DAO layer
- To connect to the database you need the following properties:
	1. JDBC (Java database connection) Driver
	2. JDBC URL
	3. User-name
	4. Password
	
	